 {\"ngram\": \"the age\", \"from\": 806, \"to\": 813}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 834, \"to\": 851}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The baron is now seen as a controversial figure due to his racist and misogynistic views.\", \"from\": 907, \"to\": 996, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The baron\", \"from\": 907, \"to\": 916}, {\"ngram\": \"a controversial figure\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 954}, {\"ngram\": \"his racist and misogynistic views\", \"from\": 962, \"to\": 995}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Coubertin described himself as a \\\"fanatical colonialist\\\", and believed that women should be excluded from the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 998, \"to\": 1122, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Coubertin\", \"from\": 998, \"to\": 1007}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"fanatical colonialist\", \"from\": 1029, \"to\": 1053}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 1074, \"to\": 1079}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1104, \"to\": 1121}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Limits on female participation reflected the prejudices of the era, including that sportswomen could lose their femininity or become sterile.\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1265, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Limits\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1130}, {\"ngram\": \"female participation\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1154}, {\"ngram\": \"the prejudices\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1179}, {\"ngram\": \"the era\", \"from\": 1183, \"to\": 1190}, {\"ngram\": \"that sportswomen\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1218}, {\"ngram\": \"their femininity\", \"from\": 1230, \"to\": 1246}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He argued that an Olympics with women would be, \\\"impractical, uninteresting (and) unaesthetic\\\".\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1362, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an Olympics\", \"from\": 1282, \"to\": 1293}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1304}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Coubertin said a year before his death: \\\"The only real Olympic hero is the individual male athlete.\", \"from\": 1364, \"to\": 1463, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Coubertin\", \"from\": 1364, \"to\": 1373}, {\"ngram\": \"his death\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1402}, {\"ngram\": \"The only real Olympic hero\", \"from\": 1405, \"to\": 1431}, {\"ngram\": \"the individual male athlete\", \"from\": 1435, \"to\": 1462}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Therefore, no women's, no team, sport.\\\"\", \"from\": 1464, \"to\": 1503, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Therefore, no women's, no team\", \"from\": 1464, \"to\": 1494}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1496, \"to\": 1501}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A descendant of Coubertin argued he was a man of his time and his views had evolved throughout his life.\", \"from\": 1505, \"to\": 1609, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A descendant\", \"from\": 1505, \"to\": 1517}, {\"ngram\": \"Coubertin\", \"from\": 1521, \"to\": 1530}, {\"ngram\": \"a man\", \"from\": 1545, \"to\": 1550}, {\"ngram\": \"his time\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1562}, {\"ngram\": \"his views\", \"from\": 1567, \"to\": 1576}, {\"ngram\": \"his life\", \"from\": 1600, \"to\": 1608}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We reduce him to writings that are shocking from today's perspective,\\\" Diane de Navacelle de Coubertin told French dailyLe Parisien.\", \"from\": 1611, \"to\": 1744, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1683, \"end\": 1688, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diane_Chambers\", \"score\": 0.9999995762037531, \"rank\": 1.6756675589887003e-07, \"text\": \"Diane\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diane_Chambers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diane_Chambers\"}, {\"begin\": 1720, \"end\": 1726, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8845248954522889, \"rank\": 0.07253244686168167, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French